dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. Directorate of Overseas Surveys.
dct_description_sm: This map is Sheet 25 Edition 2 of the topographic map series E 804 Trinidad 1:25,000. It has been scanned, cropped to the map area, and georeferenced. Contour intervals are shown at 25 meters. Sheet History: Field survey by DOS; Air photography -- Spartan Air Dervices Sept-Oct 1957 Feb 1958. RAF Oct-Nov 1964; Field revision by Lands & Surveys Dept 1969-70. Printed by Lands & Surveys Division in 1978. Published by Great Britain. Directorate of Overseas Surveys in 1970.
